Client -> Entry: open conversation
Entry -> SessionPool: getOrCreate(conversation_id)
SessionPool -> AgentSession: new AgentSession(...)
SessionPool -> AgentSession: initialize(baseConfig)
AgentSession -> ToolCatalog: refresh and resolve selection
ToolCatalog --> AgentSession: List<AgentTool>
AgentSession -> SkillLoader: scan local SKILL.md files
SkillLoader --> AgentSession: List<Skill with Path>
